alerts.description:
There is a risk of wind gusts (level 1 of 4).
Max. gusts: ~ 55 km/h; Wind direction: north-east

There is a risk of storm-force gusts (Level 2 of 4).
Height range: > 1000 m; Max. gusts: 80-100 km/h; Wind direction: north-east; Increased gusts: in exposed locations ~ 110 km/h

There is a risk of gale-force gusts (Level 2 of 4).
Height range: > 1000 m; Max. gusts: 70-85 km/h; Wind direction: north-east; Increased gusts: in exposed locations < 100 km/h

There is a risk of frost (Level 1 of 2).
Minimum temperature: ~ -2 °C
There is a slight risk of icy surfaces (level 1 of 4).

There is a risk of frost (Level 1 of 2).
Minimum temperature: -4 - -8 °C
